snippet.title: A Walk on the Wild Side
snippet.description:
Welcome to my channel A Walk on the Wild Side. I am an award winning professional photographer specialising in travel, weather & astronomy. I am also a CAA licensed drone operator. Please click on the link to my website in the bottom right corner of the banner image (Hartes) on my home screen to find out more about me and browse my photography gallery.

I post walk around video content mainly in my hometown of Blackpool, which looks at different sides of the town from rundown streets to the famous promenade, as well as capturing the various characters along the way. I will include some photography if it is convenient. Sometimes I may venture further than Blackpool to vlog in some far flung place. Watch and find out.

As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases via the links provided in video descriptions.
